<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Career Guide Quiz</title>
<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #eaeaff; /* light purple-blue */
        color: #333; /* dark grey */
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
        width: 80%;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background-color: #fff; /* white */
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1, h2 {
        color: #4b0082; /* indigo */
    }
    label {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    input[type="radio"] {
        margin-right: 10px;
    }
    button {
        background-color: #4b0082; /* indigo */
        color: #fff; /* white */
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-top: 10px;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>Career Guide Quiz</h1>
    <p>Answer the following questions to discover which career field might suit you best:</p>
    <form id="quizForm">
        <label>1. Do you enjoy working with your hands and being outdoors?</label>
        <input type="radio" name="question1" value="realistic"> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="question1" value="not_realistic"> No <br>
        
        <label>2. Are you curious and enjoy solving complex problems?</label>
        <input type="radio" name="question2" value="investigative"> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="question2" value="not_investigative"> No <br>
        
        <label>3. Do you have a creative side and enjoy expressing yourself through art or design?</label>
        <input type="radio" name="question3" value="artistic"> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="question3" value="not_artistic"> No <br>
        
        <label>4. Do you enjoy helping and working closely with others?</label>
        <input type="radio" name="question4" value="social"> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="question4" value="not_social"> No <br>
        
        <label>5. Are you ambitious and enjoy leading and persuading others?</label>
        <input type="radio" name="question5" value="enterprising"> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="question5" value="not_enterprising"> No <br>
        
        <label>6. Do you prefer working with clear guidelines and structure?</label>
        <input type="radio" name="question6" value="conventional"> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="question6" value="not_conventional"> No <br>
	
	 <label>7. Do you prefer working with gadgets?</label>
        <input type="radio" name="question7" value="realistic"> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="question7" value="not_realistic"> No <br>

	 <label>8. Analyzing a situation or thing for its pros and cons?</label>
        <input type="radio" name="question8" value="investigative"> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="question8" value="not_investigative"> No <br>

	 <label>9.Do you enjoy create or appreciating art?</label>
        <input type="radio" name="question9" value="artistic"> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="question9" value="not_artistic"> No <br>

	 <label>10.Do you relate to others feeling and problems as your own?</label>
        <input type="radio" name="question10" value="social"> Yes
        <input type="radio" name="question10" value="not_social"> No <br>
        
        <button type="button" onclick="submitQuiz()">Submit</button>
        <button type="button" onclick="redirectToSite()">Back</button>
    </form>
    <div id="result"></div>
</div>

<script>
    function submitQuiz() {
        var answers = document.querySelectorAll('input[type="radio"]:checked');
        if (answers.length < 6) {
            alert("Please answer all questions.");
            return;
        }
        
        var scores = {
            realistic: 0,
            investigative: 0,
            artistic: 0,
            social: 0,
            enterprising: 0,
            conventional: 0
        };
        
        for (var i = 0; i < answers.length; i++) {
            var value = answers[i].value;
            scores[value]++;
        }
        
        var maxScore = 0;
        var maxField = '';
        for (var field in scores) {
            if (scores[field] > maxScore) {
                maxScore = scores[field];
                maxField = field;
            }
        }
        
        var resultText = '';
        switch (maxField) {
            case 'realistic':
                resultText = 'Your results suggest a career in the Realistic field.';
                break;
            case 'investigative':
                resultText = 'Your results suggest a career in the Investigative field.';
                break;
            case 'artistic':
                resultText = 'Your results suggest a career in the Artistic field.';
                break;
            case 'social':
                resultText = 'Your results suggest a career in the Social field.';
                break;
            case 'enterprising':
                resultText = 'Your results suggest a career in the Enterprising field.';
                break;
            case 'conventional':
                resultText = 'Your results suggest a career in the Conventional field.';
                break;
            default:
                resultText = 'Your results do not match any specific field.';
                break;
        }
        
        document.getElementById('result').innerHTML = '<h2>Result:</h2>' + resultText;
    }

    function redirectToSite() {
        window.location.href = "Careertest.html"; 
    }
</script>
</body>
</html>
